{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-exhibition-js","path":"/exhibition/trust-your-technolust/","result":{"data":{"contentfulExhibition":{"title":"Trust Your Technolust","startDate":"2024-01-26","endDate":"2024-02-17","dateTbc":false,"tags":null,"subtitleShortDescription":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<p>works by LaTurbo Avedon</p>"}},"description":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Avatar-artist LaTurbo Avedon’s first solo exhibition in Berlin. Trust Your Technolust examines the wavering promises of virtual worlds through the installation of augmented reality sculptures and projection.</p>\n<p>LaTurbo invites viewers to explore past and present works from Club Rothko, a virtual nightclub rendered at the end of the metaverse.</p>\n<p>Watch the exhibition accompanying AR sculpture Always Night (2024) at panke.gallery</p>\n<p>➡️ <strong><a href=\"https://openar.art/a/De0D8TuzWYJ1tjzI\">https://openar.art/a/De0D8TuzWYJ1tjzI</a></strong></p>\n<p>Alongside the solo exhibition by LaTurbo Avedon at panke.gallery, you can also experience their geolocated AR sculpture Sky Queue (2024) at Tresor.</p>\n<p>➡️ <a href=\"https://openar.art/a/3ZX7QNeUesyOOs1k\">__https://openar.art/a/3ZX7QNeUesyOOs1k\n</a>__</p>"}},"openingHours":"Wed to Sat 3 – 7pm","vernissageInfos":"Vernissage 26 January from 7pm","furtherInformationBlocks":[{"id":"3d9ce211-47e3-553e-892e-a0fb51f634b2","title":"LaTurbo Avedon","childContentfulContentBlockBlockContentTextNode":{"id":"2bf316a8-1248-5dbe-87ad-0ac846771b24","childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<p><a href=\"https://turboavedon.com/\">LaTurbo Avedon</a> is an avatar and artist, creating work that emphasizes the practice of non-physical identity and authorship. Avedon has spent the past decade developing a body of work that illuminates the ever-growing intensity between users and the virtual, pursuing creative environments that deepen the meaning of immaterial experiences. They curate and design Panther Modern, a file-based exhibition space that encourages artists to create site-specific installations for the Internet.</p>"}}},{"id":"5b7f8f9f-6355-5161-b403-37a2f1b22b21","title":"supporters","childContentfulContentBlockBlockContentTextNode":{"id":"e46f6b5e-c1bc-5ba0-8683-27d00529be60","childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<p>This exhibions is supported by the Berlin Senate of Cluture in the frame of Basisförderung.\n<img src=\"//images.ctfassets.net/31ro1qkhyo69/1ruP7dVqAwCpB7ACmASOEu/383997a6724d4a44c2286db8028809f3/B_SEN_KuGZ_Logo_DE_H_P_1C.png\" alt=\"BerlinSenate\"></p>"}}}],"featuredImage":{"gatsbyImageData":{"images":{"sources":[{"srcSet":"https://images.ctfassets.net/31ro1qkhyo69/fJGYHdkmq5EB3rbFomvfT/b7fed0aa65bd2a060e5d0fa317361b25/TYTL-Social-16-9-Export-NoText_web.jpg?w=750&h=422&q=100&fm=webp&bg=transparent 750w,\nhttps://images.ctfassets.net/31ro1qkhyo69/fJGYHdkmq5EB3rbFomvfT/b7fed0aa65bd2a060e5d0fa317361b25/TYTL-Social-16-9-Export-NoText_web.jpg?w=1050&h=591&q=100&fm=webp&bg=transparent 1050w,\nhttps://images.ctfassets.net/31ro1qkhyo69/fJGYHdkmq5EB3rbFomvfT/b7fed0aa65bd2a060e5d0fa317361b25/TYTL-Social-16-9-Export-NoText_web.jpg?w=1080&h=608&q=100&fm=webp&bg=transparent 1080w,\nhttps://images.ctfassets.net/31ro1qkhyo69/fJGYHdkmq5EB3rbFomvfT/b7fed0aa65bd2a060e5d0fa317361b25/TYTL-Social-16-9-Export-NoText_web.jpg?w=1366&h=769&q=100&fm=webp&bg=transparent 1366w,\nhttps://images.ctfassets.net/31ro1qkhyo69/fJGYHdkmq5EB3rbFomvfT/b7fed0aa65bd2a060e5d0fa317361b25/TYTL-Social-16-9-Export-NoText_web.jpg?w=1920&h=1081&q=100&fm=webp&bg=transparent 1920w","sizes":"(min-width: 1050px) 1050px, 100vw","type":"image/webp"}],"fallback":{"src":"https://images.ctfassets.net/31ro1qkhyo69/fJGYHdkmq5EB3rbFomvfT/b7fed0aa65bd2a060e5d0fa317361b25/TYTL-Social-16-9-Export-NoText_web.jpg?w=1050&h=591&fl=progressive&q=100&fm=jpg&bg=transparent","srcSet":"https://images.ctfassets.net/31ro1qkhyo69/fJGYHdkmq5EB3rbFomvfT/b7fed0aa65bd2a060e5d0fa317361b25/TYTL-Social-16-9-Export-NoText_web.jpg?w=750&h=422&fl=progressive&q=100&fm=jpg&